Directives/TableofContents.html">ISO/IEC=20
      JTC 1 Directives, 5th edition, version 3.0</A>.&nbsp; =
JTC001-N-8557,=20
      2007-04-05.&nbsp; 1696kB <A=20
      =
href=3D"http://isotc.iso.org/livelink/livelink/fetch/2000/2122/327993/755=
