F=20
      download</A> available for download at ISO/IEC JTC1 Public =
Information, <A=20
      =
href=3D"http://isotc.iso.org/livelink/livelink?func=3Dll&amp;objId=3D2541=
871&amp;objAction=3Dbrowse&amp;sort=3Dname">Procedural=20
      Documentation</A>.</P>
      <P>[<STRONG>update 2008-03-17T19:45Z:</STRONG> I received a very =
helpful=20
      e-mail through the NIST Media Relations Office, pointing me to the =

      relevant sections of the JTC1 directives.&nbsp; The selections, =
summaries,=20
      and interpretation are all mine.</P>
      <P>&nbsp;<STRONG>update 2008-03-16T15:45Z:</STRONG> I learned from =
an <A=20
      =
href=3D"http://www.computerworld.com/action/article.do?command=3DviewArti=
cleBasic&amp;articleId=3D9068498&amp;intsrc=3Dnews_ts_head">Eric=20
      Lai Computerworld article</A> that AIM Global and Qualcomm are =
apparently=20
      new members of the INCITS Executive Board.&nbsp; I updated my =
observation=20
      about that and who are voting members accordingly.]</P></SMALL>
